Kit quickly feels herself being lifted up, with a sharp pain in her ankles. As she lands on the ground, she twists in the air and lands on her knees on the forest floor. She staggers to her feet, pushing the pain away.

"Haha.. I doubt that.. fool.. when all you do is ankle-biting!" She barks harshly..

She puts away her gun, and extends her claws on her hands. With a grin she runs up, going for slashing the claws at his face, aiming for his optics..
